    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/9b4926fb05bdcee13f86eab845562dad.avif?t=1771533538\" width=616 height=95 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/f767b0a91d4af47857b3dd0afa717687.poster.avif?t=1771533538\" width=608 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/f767b0a91d4af47857b3dd0afa717687.webm?t=1771533538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/f767b0a91d4af47857b3dd0afa717687.mp4?t=1771533538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/ed0692c507f9e562e53da5f1bbf58408.webp?t=1771533538\" width=616 height=17 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演一位名叫冈纳的年轻勇士，在父亲格里普首领被斯坦纳·飞矛无情杀害之后，你也被迫踏上流亡之路。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如今的冈纳家园被毁、族人也流落四方，他必须在你的指引下重建定居点、缔结战略联盟，率领手下战将锲而不舍地寻求复仇。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/136fae9c443904cfc950fd481f58e678.avif?t=1771533538\" width=616 height=95 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/23a1ed61b85b40da6b78d910d6255e60.poster.avif?t=1771533538\" width=608 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/23a1ed61b85b40da6b78d910d6255e60.webm?t=1771533538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/23a1ed61b85b40da6b78d910d6255e60.mp4?t=1771533538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/ed0692c507f9e562e53da5f1bbf58408.webp?t=1771533538\" width=616 height=17 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投身回合制战斗，战斗中的走位、单位联动以及地形都极为重要。充分利用地势高度、侧翼包抄与环境灾害，获得战局优势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位勇士都具备独特的技能组合。将他们部署在战略要地，方能掌控局势、智取敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募并训练不同类型的战士，他们各自具有可定制的装备和可升级的技能，为你提供多种多样的战术选项。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/ad8626fa84c8418938a8727a683ef323.avif?t=1771533538\" width=616 height=95 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/d146f0867fd82727f79e789d7446cb82.poster.avif?t=1771533538\" width=608 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/d146f0867fd82727f79e789d7446cb82.webm?t=1771533538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/d146f0867fd82727f79e789d7446cb82.mp4?t=1771533538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/ed0692c507f9e562e53da5f1bbf58408.webp?t=1771533538\" width=616 height=17 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >见证你的维京村落日益壮大，从小型营地发展为大型要塞。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为村民分配角色、管理资源，并升级建筑来解锁全新单位和装备。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在荒野中搜寻材料、与盟友进行贸易，并采集关键资源来制作符合史实的武器与护甲。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级你的铁匠铺、军械库与作坊，获得能够直接影响战斗能力与村民韧性的高级装备。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/2548db0b5d086404c2d11c08f4da3921.avif?t=1771533538\" width=616 height=95 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/97b68eb1c14b7f3bc2c5ec60f5d0fee1.poster.avif?t=1771533538\" width=608 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/97b68eb1c14b7f3bc2c5ec60f5d0fee1.webm?t=1771533538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/97b68eb1c14b7f3bc2c5ec60f5d0fee1.mp4?t=1771533538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/ed0692c507f9e562e53da5f1bbf58408.webp?t=1771533538\" width=616 height=17 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会引领冈纳走向胜利、恢复父亲的历史地位，还是会让狡诈的叛徒斯坦纳为你的传奇画上句号？同胞们的命运就掌握在你的手中。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《NORSE: Oath of Blood》的游戏脚本由畅销作家吉尔斯·克里斯蒂安操刀，将带你体验一段难以忘怀的沉浸式传奇，你的抉择将决定一个民族的命运。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054690/extras/8607c375c67cc685304985a2bf87ad91.avif?t=1771533538\" width=616 height=165 /></span></p>",
